Regulation Name(s): Calculator/data processing module, for clinical use
Instrument(s)/Platform(s): Freestyle Freedom Lite Blood Glucose Monitoring Systems
Method(s)/Technology(ies): Data upload from meters via serial/USB/Micro-USB cable
Document Summary: FDA 510(k) summary for Freestyle Auto-Assist Software Version 2.0, a diabetes data management software for uploading and analyzing blood glucose and ketone meter data
Indications for Use Summary: Aids people with diabetes in reviewing, analyzing, and evaluating blood glucose results, ketone test results, insulin doses, and exercise data uploaded from compatible meters to support diabetes health management; not intended for diagnosis or screening of diabetes mellitus
